fields.name: Ryzen 5 3600
fields.description: The AMD Ryzen 5 3600 is a 6-core, 12-thread processor based on the Zen 2 microarchitecture. It features 32MB of L3 cache and uses a 65W TDP. The Ryzen 5 3600 is the successor to the Ryzen 5 2600 and was released in July 2019.
